ash wednesday service with imposition of ashes events at stanford ash wednesday service with imposition of ashes facebook twitter email print add to calendar please join us for this annual interdenominational ash wednesday service hosted by the office for religious life with participation from a variety of christian voices and communities on campus this service features a short reflection prayers readings hymns and organ blessing with ashes and a ritual of repentance turning our lives back toward god as we begin the holy season of lent when wednesday february 22 2012 12 00 pm approximate duration of 1 hour s where memorial church map audience general public faculty staff students alumni friends tags religious event sponsor office for religious life contact 723 1762 religious life stanford edu admission free and welcoming to all permalink http events stanford edu events 310 31007 more info last modified february 8 2012
